x-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">CaraMaria</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Safe Bulkers (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SB\" title=\"Safe Bulkers, Inc.\">SB</a></span>) is what I consider to be the David of dry bulk shippers. At just $380 million market cap, it is among my personal favorites in the sector, for a variety of reasons. The last time I wrote about the </p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/139540669/image_139540669.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745753-safe-bulkers-maintaining-buy-rating-on-this-quality-shipper", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 11:13:10", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745750", "title": "Axos: Fed's Hawkish Forecast Hits Two Birds With One Stone", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2086436224/image_2086436224.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Online payment concept. Over shoulder view of a woman accessing a mobile banking app on her smartphone, highlighting the ease of digital finance management. Internet bank, money transaction, fintech,\" data-id=\"2086436224\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"964px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2086436224/image_2086436224.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2086436224/image_2086436224.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2086436224/image_2086436224.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2086436224/image_2086436224.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, ht