ould Be An Ideal Buying Opportunity For Clover Health", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148728482/image_2148728482.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='Close-up Shot of a Doctor\"s Hand Pointing on Brain Scan Images on Digital Tablet' data-id=\"2148728482\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148728482/image_2148728482.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148728482/image_2148728482.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148728482/image_2148728482.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148728482/image_2148728482.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148728482/image_2148728482.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148728482/image_2148728482.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148728482/image_2148728482.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148728482/image_2148728482.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Tom Werner</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Healthcare is becoming increasingly big business across the world, as ageing populations demand more and more resources by the year. Nowhere is this more accentuated that the U.S., where the healthcare and insurance landscape means that depending on which side</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com